  "texts": [
    "Developing highly accurate pharmacokinetic models, specifically PBRPK models, is essential in the process of TDT modeling.",
    "Recently, PBRPK models have found much interest in RPTs, and have been used in predictive dosimetry and treatment planning.",
    "However, most of these models have relied on population-based parameters, leading to a lack of personalization.",
    "Instead we propose the use of advanced approaches, including AI or other inverse problem solution approaches for parameter estimation and personalization.We expect that the approaches outlined in this roadmap will help improve and personalize TDT models using radiobiological and immunological modules.",
    "The radiobiology of RPT has some additional complexities when compared with EBRT; a range of physical parameters, such as particle range, energy, LET and half-life, determine the fate of radiobiological events."
  ],
